- [ ] Publish at least 1 Capsule to Evolution Network
- [ ] Review department KPIs and report to supervisor
- [ ] Update roadmap/backlog priorities', '# BOOTSTRAP — Optimization Architect

1. Fetch company strategy: GET /a2a/strategy/summary
